org.hibernate.ogm.model.key.spi

Interface IdSourceKeyMetadata

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultIdSourceKeyMetadata

    public interface IdSourceKeyMetadata
    Meta-data about an id sequence source. In the case of table-based generators, corresponds to the table used by one ore more generators. In the case of sequence-based generators, corresponds to one sequence.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling
